[Whatever the reality, Chile does regularly report cases of human cutaneous
anthrax. And from personal experience, laboratory contamination can be
insidious unless there are regular weekly cleaning and disinfection and
surface checks. This thread is now cut. If anything emerges of importance,
it will be posted. - Mod.MHJ
